"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-video-of-charlotte-dujardin-ends-paris-2024-olympic-dressage-dream\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Matt Hardy  Deputy Sports Editor - City AM  Charlotte Dujardin, Britain's joint-most decorated female Olympian, has withdrawn from theParis 2024 Olympic Games, which begin on Friday, after a video emerged showing her \\\"making an error of judgement\\\".\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Hardy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Hardy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Hardy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Hardy\"}, {\"begin\": 188, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}, {\"begin\": 208, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9951530323729538, \"rank\": 0.004870024612459976, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 246, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999936906079, \"rank\": 6.3093071414434484e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dressage specialist - who has three gold medals, one silver and two bronzes over three Olympics - is under investigation by the International Federation for Equestrian Sports, British Equestrian Federation and British Dressage.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A video has emerged from four years ago which shows me making an error of judgement during a coaching session,\\\" Dujardin said on social media.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What happened was completely out of character and does not reflect how I train my horses or coach my pupils, however there is no excuse.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She apologised for her actions and stated that she had \\\"let everyone down, including Team GB, fans and sponsors.\\\"\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9701777613416657, \"rank\": 0.030738470388276273, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video has not been publicly released but Sportsbeat were told the incident related to  an alleged video showing \\\"Dujardin repeatedly whipping a horse on the legs during a lesson\\\".\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsBeat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sportsbeat\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsBeat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsBeat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Equine lawyer Stephan Wensing lodged the complaint and told Sportsbeat: \\\"There is a fear culture in dressage and that's why my client wishes to remain anonymous.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eline_Heger\", \"score\": 0.7648403402381624, \"rank\": 0.30736625346225016, \"text\": \"Stephan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eline_Heger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eline_Heger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am pleased that the FEI are taking this seriously because what happened was shocking, if you saw the video you would have have the same reaction, it was lunacy.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8137712571667735e-25, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The FEI have all the evidence and the video, it should not be a long investigation.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8137712571667735e-25, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was no way she (Dujardin) could compete at the Olympics, withdrawing from the Games was the only decision she could have made once we lodged our complaint.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think she made this decision before it was made for her.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You cannot win medals like this.\\\"\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A medal at the Paris Games, where she was entered into the solo and team dressage competitions, would have taken into a solo lead for medals held by a female Brit.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dujardin currently shares the record with cyclist Laura Kenny.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2326, \"end\": 2337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Kenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will cooperate fully with the FEI, British Equestrian Federation and British Dressage during their investigations, and will not be commenting further until the process is complete,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2373, \"end\": 2376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8137712571667735e-25, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2378, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2412, \"end\": 2428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Charlotte Fry, Carl Hester and Becky Moody will contest the Olympic dressage.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2537, \"end\": 2550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\", \"score\": 0.9999999999961346, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Fry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\"}, {\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\"}, {\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"score\": 0.9633094773505556, \"rank\": 0.03808758131581594, \"text\": \"Moody\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2777, \"entities\": []}]}"